    "If you have previously purchased a subscription on another device, you can restore your subscription by clicking the \"Restore Purchase\" button below. Please make sure you are using the same Apple ID used for the purchase." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果您之前在其他设备上购买过订阅,可以通过点击下方的\"恢复购买\"按钮来恢复您的订阅。请确保您使用的是购买时所用的Apple ID 账号。"
          }
        },
        "zh-HK" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果您之前在其他設備上購買過訂閱,可以通過點擊下方的\"恢復購買\"按鈕來恢復您的訂閱。請確保您使用的是購買時所用的Apple ID 賬號。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
